    "long_instructions": "#### Layering Lyrics\r\n\r\nMilo needs help making a song with only lyrics! Create a  10-measure backbeat that only uses lyrics to make something unexpected. \r\n\r\nChallenge: Try to recreate this timline that plays one sound, then overlaps the same sound before it's done.\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/60a1f6188af913cc3da589748adbc393-image-1741728188516.22.57 PM.png)",
